[Reclines on the settee.

Give me an ash tray.

[HEINRICH gives it to him.

All right; go along.

HEINRICH

Beg your pardon, sir       

KARL, seated on couch L.

What is it?

HEINRICH

Mimi is here.

KARL

Where?

HEINRICH

Waiting in the studio.

KARL, indifferent, reading newspaper

