Hallo.

[KARL is silent, continues reading his paper.



[MIMI comes down L.

Don't you want to work today?

KARL

No.



[Continues reading paper.

[HEINRICH goes into the studio.

MIMI, in bad humor, crosses to C.

Good-bye.



[Turns around.

And tomorrow?

KARL

No.

MIMI, sad

Good-bye. (Wipes her eyes.) You don't love me any more
... you don't love me any more.

KARL

Oh! It's going to start again!

MIMI

Ever since last fall you've been different. I knew it right
