KARL



[Coming back, closes the door, stands still for
a minute       when he comes back, OLGA shivers
slightly and touches her forehead with her hand.

[Crosses to L. C. by OLGA.

What is it?

OLGA, with a nervous, soft laugh

Nothing       nothing at all.

KARL, tenderly

Are you frightened?



[OLGA does not answer.

Tell me.

OLGA, nervous, confused, as if she was afraid of him

I don't know, but       I feel as if       as if       

KARL

What do you mean?

OLGA, trying to laugh, but very nervously

I had the same feeling once in Dresden, when my mother took
